type: Tutorial Step - Make sure You’re Comfortable

definition.text: Before you jump into governance, it’s important you know what is being governed!

paragraphs.text: We have got a lot of exciting things to talk about, but I want to make sure you can follow along easily.
If you haven't already, take some time to go through the Getting Started Tutorials.
There is no need to be an expert, but some general knowledge of the system will make your time in the Governance project much more productive.
